A bot which can randomly check a website links and forms for errors.

$ python proto.py http://example.com
$ python proto.py --html=w3c http://example.com
$ python proto.py --stress http://example.com.localdomain

$ python proto.py --help
Usage: proto.py [options] start_url

Options:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  -q, --quiet           don't print many status messages to stdout
  --silent              output as least as possible
  -d, --debug           print status messages to stdout
  -t SURF_TIMER, --timer=SURF_TIMER
                        time between requests
  -c MAX_COUNT, --max-count=MAX_COUNT
                        max number of page loads
  --check-dash          report # links
  --forms               use forms
  --links               follow links
  --html=HTML_VALIDATOR
                        html validation method (use no to disable)
  --cookie=COOKIE       cookie (name=value)
  -o, --once            visit only once
  --threads=THREADS     bots to run in parallel
  --stress              default parameters for load test
  --heavy               default parameters for load test
